				<td colspan="2"><span>Slot 1 - only augs that fit in slot 1 are ones that are any slot.
<br />
Slot 2/3 - ldon armor slots.
<br />
Slot 4 - Normal weapon slots.
<br />
Slot 5/6 - ldon weapon slots.
<br />
Slot 7 - Pretty much any non time/ldon bought armor.
<br />
Slot 8 - Time or higher gear.
<br />

<br />

<br />
This is a rough overview of the aug slots ... there could be a few select items that fall out of category or have more than one slot.</span></td>
