				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, actually &quot;destroy&quot; isn't really accurate.  The solvents &quot;remove&quot; the aug, and allow you to move it to a different piece of gear.
<br />

<br />
But, yes, the solvent needed is specific to the type of aug you're removing.  The higher level the aug stone, the more expensive the solvent to remove it.  Each aug stone's description information tells which class of solvent is used to remove it.  Aug removal solvents can only be purchased (with plat) from a vendor at the Butcherblock Wayfarer Camp.
